Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,走了  泉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,邁爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,心率已經很低了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,再繼續的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有詢問你的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,做家犬真是不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,IBM還能放出來幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是0次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你很擔心戶崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但你千萬要冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡  有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,緊急電源怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?  咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,保險栓  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是bravo1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,起居室已控制
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,控制敵人!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,room C clear
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,room D clear
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,還剩room E和F
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,α1  收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,別磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,咱倆  今天都不太走運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,戶崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡  位置怎麼暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,比起這個  先向國內…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:36.71,Comment,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪你讓那個女人逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,懲罰一分都別想少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,連選條像樣的路都不會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真想現在就給你打一針
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他們人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20\pos(377,436}safe house
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,還在秘密基地附近的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,他們剛在第二個拐彎處右轉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我們別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你們負責善後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們繞到前面去  夾擊他們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒這樣的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你不聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,泉小姐  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,從右邊繞過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,泉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,戶崎先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,正在追
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,追得上嗎  永井
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  永井
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我閉會嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,情況不妙  平澤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他們的前進方向上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是美國大使館
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.29,0:22:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這是所有情況中最壞的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?  什麼最壞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大使館是徹徹底底的治外法權
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是警察還是自衛隊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,都不能對其出手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.34,0:22:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他們逃進大使館的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才問為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.89,0:22:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我安靜會
